doc: ColorScheme represents which kind of theme shall be rendered.

0.name: SizeClassSmall
0.doc: SizeClassSmall are devices below 640 dp screen width.

1.name: SizeClassMedium
1.doc: SizeClassMedium are devices below 768dp screen width.

2.name: SizeClassLarge
2.doc: SizeClassLarge are devices below 1024dp screen width.

3.name: SizeClassXL
3.doc: SizeClassXL are devices below 1280dp screen width.

4.name: SizeClass2XL
4.doc: SizeClass2XL are devices below 1536dp screen width.
